hotel_name: Group Villa VIP H Bi Vng Tu

hotel_text.important_information: A damage deposit of VND 5000000 is required on arrival. This will be collected as a cash payment. You should be reimbursed on check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full, in cash, subject to an inspection of the property.

policies.content: You'll be charged 30% of the total price if you cancel your booking.

All children are welcome. 4 children under 3 years stay free of charge when using existing beds.
4 children from 3 to 7 year are charged  VND 200000 per night when using existing beds.
4 children from 7 to 18 year are charged  VND 250000 per night when using existing beds.
One child under 7 years is charged VND 500000  per night in a crib.
One child under 18 years is charged VND 200000  per night in an extra bed.
The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 54.
The maximum number of cribs in a room is 1.
Any type of extra bed or crib is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in all areas and is free of charge.
Free private parking is available  on site (reservation is not needed).
Pets are allowed. Charges may apply.
No prepayment is needed.
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
10 % VAT is included. VND 5,000,000 Damage deposit per stay is excluded. A City tax is not applicable.
items: VND 5,000,000 Damage deposit per stay is excluded.
